// Forked from chromium/src/ui/events/keycodes/dom/keycode_converter_data.inc.
// Trimmed to fields we need: (win_scan, mac_vk, win_vk, code, dom_key, loc).
//   win_scan : Windows scan code; high byte is 0xE0/0xE1 for extended keys.
//   mac_vk   : macOS Carbon virtual key code, or 0xFFFF if not present.
//   win_vk   : Windows VK code — also the legacy DOM `keyCode`.
//   code     : DOM `code` string.
//   dom_key  : DOM `key` for non-text keys; "" for keys that produce text.
//   loc      : DOM location — 0=standard, 1=left, 2=right, 3=numpad.

